      <title>雅宝、康明斯在拜登的清洁能源推动下获得税收抵免</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/albemarle-cummins-receive-tax-credits-under-bidens-clean-energy-drive-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国能源部 (DOE) 周五公布的详细信息，雅保 (Albemarle)、康明斯 (Cummins) 和西门子能源 (Siemens Energy) 等公司根据《通货膨胀削减法案》(IRA) 的一部分获得了税收抵免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/albemarle-cummins-receive-tax-credits-under-bidens-clean-energy-drive-2024-04-19/</guid>
