      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-streets-fear-gauge-over-5-month-high-rate-cut-mideast-worries-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:29:15 GMT</pubDate>
